# As of pnpm v11, .npmrc is only read for auth/registry settings; every
# other setting (node-linker, strict-peer-dependencies, auto-install-peers,
# etc.) must live in pnpm-workspace.yaml instead (see nodeLinker there for
# why hoisting is required). The lines below are intentionally not
# duplicated here since pnpm v11 ignores them in this file.
